### ⚙️ Admin Management Endpoints
# Complete administrative control panel for system management
# ALL endpoints require ADMIN authentication via secure HttpOnly cookies

@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:5000

### =============================================
### ADMIN LOGIN (REQUIRED FIRST)
### =============================================

### Login as Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "StrongPass123!"
}

### =============================================
### SYSTEM ANALYTICS & OVERVIEW
### =============================================

### Get System Statistics Dashboard
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/stats
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: access_token_cookie=YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### =============================================
### PROJECT MODERATION
### =============================================

### Get All Pending Projects for Review
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/projects/pending
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: access_token_cookie=YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Pending Projects with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/projects/pending?page=1&per_page=5
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: access_token_cookie=YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Approve Project
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/projects/1/approve
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: access_token_cookie=YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Feature Project (Makes it highlighted)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/projects/1/feature
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: access_token_cookie=YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Un-feature Project (Toggle off)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/projects/1/feature
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: access_token_cookie=YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Reject Project with Reason
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/projects/2/reject
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: access_token_cookie=YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "reason": "Project does not meet quality standards. Issues found: 1) Incomplete documentation, 2) Missing error handling, 3) Security vulnerabilities in authentication. Please address these issues and resubmit."
}

